8jjGTp7M4FbivX3mHXJ6da.jpg","b":"/4jauQUVs9zwpOJgTSlAgmfbVeRf.jpg","t":"黑板","r":6.6,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-09-01","hs":0.182,"d":0.366,"mt":"movie","o":"在两伊战争时期，一群逃难的教师背着黑板在荒原上行走，他们中间有一个叫萨义德（萨义德•莫哈默迪Said Mohamadi 饰）的男人，胸怀非常远大的抱负，那就是让村里的孩子都能阅读，通过知识改变自己的命运，摆脱窘迫的困境。为此，他放弃了跟富家女成亲的机会，毅然决然地踏上了教授孩子读书的道路。他和同伴为了生计，脱离了大部队。萨义德后来终于收了一位好学的弟子，在成年人赌博的时候，他教弟子写下名字、爱等字眼，然而谁想师徒二人遭到飞来横祸……萨义德的同伴遇到了一群迷路的伊拉克难民，后者出钱要他做向导，从此他的人生轨迹得以转变。这两个教师多舛的命运仿佛是那个时代挥之不去的阴影……\r 本片获得第56届戛纳国际电影节获评委会奖。"},{"id":16171,"p":"/gTzWCN5g1eSS7pLH6lgVzLdr25J.jpg","b":"/dYNY6tKcU50zpIT0zFMgUJroODj.jpg","t":"托马斯·卡兹的九次人生","r":6.5,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-03-01","hs":0.182,"d":0.365,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":125709,"p":"/n7X4jmmRIRtqNQWXJt8LxZcS1Ja.jpg","b":"/1VYE83DZuMrkmc5w364oeYDzYwK.jpg","t":"Joe Gould's Secret","r":6.1,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-01-21","hs":0.182,"d":0.365,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":15665,"p":"/r84Qve8mVeDXBKnSnBSQIS2OaD.jpg","b":"/xzCoEGF3wPRsz2tuCLb9pGLTRDp.jpg","t":"The Eyes of Tammy Faye","r":6.2,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-01-25","hs":0.181,"d":0.364,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":36380,"p":"/4FGCC1CkEr1EvI3OJnSnzF53uNp.jpg","b":"/zJrfbt8FJ7wgDuHz2tYCH0idwIp.jpg","t":"Chłopaki nie płaczą","r":7.4,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-02-25","hs":0.18,"d":0.358,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":18153,"p":"/wEylWTGRZoOR51wo422rhYXkV6Y.jpg","b":null,"t":"Steal This Movie","r":5.656,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-08-18","hs":0.179,"d":0.36,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":44069,"p":"/m4n5p7icLut5Dv8tlFJcPE80XKW.jpg","b":"/ms42duZvrOKa4TSU9b3nmW1BPfl.jpg","t":"女人三部曲","r":6.1,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-09-01","hs":0.177,"d":0.355,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":252724,"p":"/5JSjMbkKoOuZlqGVWJ6PhAa1JkQ.jpg","b":"/A8hE7xznQBEpCdDGxivzDdCxxgg.jpg","t":"Mary and Rhoda","r":6,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-02-07","hs":0.171,"d":0.339,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":49325,"p":"/sUTLjiYHTOdudFGLdiFY966WKG3.jpg","b":"/5eyfRHuHEAv66TciacfFD7HOs28.jpg","t":"Lek","r":6.3,"y":2000,"rd":"2000-07-15","hs":0.169,"d":0.336,"mt":"movie","o":""},{"id":67385,"p":"/3WBoL2upB5PlopSqd13ffN0a0zl.jpg","b":"/5m2HJSI5mm